%20media%20is%20the%20best%20platform%20to%20reach%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20it%20is%20his%20social%20media%20criticism%20of%20a%20senior%20officer%20that%20landed%20him%20in%20trouble%20and%20led%20to%20the%20government%20action%20against%20him.%20The%202007-batch%20IAS%20officer%20described%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%20A%20Jayathilak%20as%20a%20psychopath%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20orchestrating%20baseless%20news%20reports%20against%20him.%20Following%20the%20state%20government's%20action%2C%20the%20officer%20has%20said%20he%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhistleblower%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20being%20an%20IAS%20officer%20was%20not%20his%20sole%20ambition%20and%20he%20had%20other%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20'Collector%20Bro'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EN%20Prashanth%20is%20from%20Thalassery%20in%20Kerala's%20Kannur%20district.%20He%20studied%20at%20Loyola%20School%20and%20Government%20Law%20College%20in%20Thiruvanathapuram.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20complete%20a%20degree%20in%20banking%20law%20before%20joining%20IAS%20in%202007.%20After%20serving%20multiple%20roles%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20Kozhikode%20district%20collector%20in%202015.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20stint%20that%20he%20was%20described%20as%20'Collector%20Bro'%20for%20his%20social%20media%20interactions%20with%20people%20and%20his%20unique%20initiatives.%20One%20such%20initiative%20that%20grabbed%20attention%20was%20a%20Facebook%20message%20in%20which%20he%20asked%20people%20for%20help%20to%20clean%20a%2014-acre%20lake.%20He%20promised%20the%20volunteers%20a%20plate%20of%20Malabar%20biryani.%20Several%20volunteers%20responded%20to%20the%20call%20and%20were%20rewarded%20with%20a%20biryani%20treat%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20wrote%20a%20book%2C%20Collector%20Bro%3A%20The%20quixotic%20'thallals'%20of%20a%20civil%20servant%2C%20describing%20his%20experience%20of%20leading%20the%20Kozhikode%20district%20administration.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20rose%20to%20the%20post%20of%20Special%20Secretary%20in%20the%20SC%2FST%20Development%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Outburst%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Prashanth%20has%20levelled%20serious%20allegations%20against%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%20Jayathilak.%20He%20has%20described%20the%20senior%20bureaucrat%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpsychopath%26quot%3B%20and%20alleged%20that%20he%20ruined%20the%20lives%20of%20subordinates%20who%20did%20not%20follow%20his%20instructions.%20The%20trigger%20for%20the%20outburst%20was%20a%20media%20report%20that%20claimed%20several%20files%20of%20'Unnathi'%20--%20an%20initiative%20aimed%20at%20the%20welfare%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20--%20went%20missing%20during%20Mr%20Prashanth's%20tenure%20as%20its%20CEO.%20The%20IAS%20officer%20trashed%20the%20allegations%20and%20accused%20Mr%20Jayathilak%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20reporter%26quot%3B%20who%20was%20allegedly%20undermining%20him%20by%20planting%20fake%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20suspension%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20told%20a%20TV%20channel%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20new%20experience%20for%20me.%20Criticising%20the%20government%20or%20its%20policies%20is%20wrong%20and%20action%20can%20be%20taken.%20I%20don't%20think%20anyone%20will%20be%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20I%20have%20done%20anything%20like%20that.%20My%20criticism%20was%20aimed%20at%20certain%20individuals'%20inappropriate%20tendencies%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20fabricated%20reports.%20Evidence%20has%20also%20come%20to%20light%20regarding%20this.%20I%20trust%20that%20creating%20fake%20reports%20is%20not%20a%20government%20policy%2C%20but%20if%20criticising%20such%20actions%20leads%20to%20consequences%2C%20that's%20news%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Political%20Backdrop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20against%20N%20Prashanth%20is%20also%20playing%20out%20against%20a%20political%20backdrop.%20CPM%20leader%20and%20former%20Fisheries%20Minister%20J%20Mercykutty%20Amma%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20IAS%20officer%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20political%20conspiracy%20against%20her.%20The%20plot%2C%20she%20alleged%20was%20hatched%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Ramesh%20Chennithala%20and%20N%20Prashanth%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20his%20private%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20Kerala%20is%20witnessing%20the%20fallout%20of%20Shri%20Prashanth%20IAS%20breaking%20all%20service%20rules%20and%20common%20decency.%20But%20back%20in%20February%202021%2C%20Prasanth%20played%20the%20villain%20in%20a%20political%20conspiracy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20referred%20to%20Mr%20Chennithala's%20allegation%20that%20the%20Fisheries%20Department%2C%20then%20under%20her%2C%20sanctioned%20a%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20deep-sea%20trawler%20deal.%20%26quot%3BThis%20news%20stirred%20up%20controversy.%20When%20reporters%20asked%20me%2C%20I%20clarified%20that%20no%20such%20deal%20had%20taken%20place.%20Ramesh%20Chennithala%20released%20a%20document%20supposedly%20showing%20that%20an%20MoU%20had%20been%20signed...%20Chennithala%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20the%20Fisheries%20Department%20had%20signed%20the%20MoU%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20it%20was%20signed%20by%20Prasanth%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20Mercykutty%20Amma%20lost%20the%202021%20polls%20in%20Kundara%2C%20which%20she%20has%20represented%20thrice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20row%2C%20the%20Congress-led%20UDF%20has%20said%20government%20officers%20in%20Kerala%20are%20fighting%20each%20other%20under%20the%20Left%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731398640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fa2qerpt_n-prashanth-ias_625x300_12_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fn-prashanth-kerala-ias-officer-collector-bro-to-suspended-whistleblower-ker