20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao.%20He%20is%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Delhi%2C%20during%20which%20he%20met%20Union%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Affairs%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20and%20flagged%20alleged%20corruption%20involving%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20AMRUT%20scheme%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAMRUT%20--%20Atal%20Mission%20for%20Rejuvenation%20and%20Urban%20Transformation%20(AMRUT)%20--%20focuses%20on%20development%20of%20basic%20infrastructure%20in%20selected%20cities%20in%20the%20sectors%20of%20water%20supply%3B%20sewerage%2C%20drainage%2C%20green%20spaces%20and%20parks%20and%20non-motorised%20transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKTR%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20was%20facilitating%20corruption%20in%20AMRUT%20tenders%20to%20benefit%20a%20company%20linked%20to%20Revanth%20Reddy's%20brother-in-law%20Sujan%20Reddy.%20He%20has%20said%20the%20company%2C%20Sodha%20Constructions%2C%20recorded%20a%20meagre%20profit%20in%20the%20years%20before%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Telangana%20and%20lacks%20the%20credentials%20to%20handle%20such%20large%20projects.%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20tender%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20the%20BRS%20leader%20said%20he%20hoped%20that%20the%20Centre%20would%20take%20action.%20%26quot%3BThis%20company%20lacks%20necessary%20qualifications.%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20example%20of%20crony%20capitalism.%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20fight%20against%20each%20other%2C%20but%20in%20Telangana%20i%20see%20Ajab%20Prem%20Ki%20Gazab%20Kahani.%20The%20BJP%20sits%20quietly%20against%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Telangana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20While%20the%20Congress%20holds%2076%20seats%20in%20the%20119-member%20Telangana%20Assembly%2C%20the%20BRS%20is%20the%20main%20Opposition%20with%2028%20MLAs.%20The%20BJP%20holds%20eight%20seats%20in%20the%20House.%20Earlier%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%20brother-in-law%20had%20sued%20KTR%20for%20defamation%20over%20his%20social%20media%20posts%20alleging%20corruption%20in%20the%20tender%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Revenue%20Minister%20said%20the%20BRS%20leader%20had%20travelled%20to%20Delhi%20to%20seek%20the%20help%20of%20%26quot%3Bbigwigs%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20questioned%20if%20Mr%20Rao%20was%20in%20Delhi%20to%20%26quot%3Bplead%26quot%3B%20with%20Union%20ministers%20to%20withdraw%20charges%20against%20him%20in%20the%20Formula-E%20race%20funds%20transfer%20case.%20The%20minister%20accused%20KTR%20of%20diverting%20Rs%2055%20crore%20to%20a%20Formula-E%20racing%20company%20without%20the%20cabinet's%20approval.%20The%20matter%20is%20now%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20state%20police's%20anti-corruption%20bureau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20Congress%20unseated%20the%20BRS%20to%20form%20the%20government%20in%20Telangana%20last%20year%2C%20multiple%20issues%20have%20triggered%20heated%20exchanges%20between%20KTR%20and%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20Many%20of%20these%20exchanges%20have%20also%20escalated%20to%20personal%20attacks%2C%20with%20KTR%20referring%20to%20Mr%20Reddy%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BCheap%20Minister%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Congress%20leader%20saying%20that%20KTR%20is%20%26quot%3Bday-dreaming%26quot%3B%20that%20his%20party%20will%20return%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731398040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fatt6spo8_ktr_625x300_24_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fktr-revanth-reddy-telangana-ajab-prem-ki-ktr-alleges-a-bjp-congress-love-affair-in-telangana-7000244%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20fight%20against%20each%20other%20across%20the%20country%2C%20but%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrange%20love%20story%26quot%3B%20in%20Telangana%2C%20former%20state%20minister%20and%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20leader%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20told%20NDTV%20today%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22