0Real%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20few%20days%20back%2C%20a%20few%20educated%20middle-class%20people%20in%20Bengaluru%20lost%20their%20life's%20earnings%20to%20deepfakes%20of%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Mukesh%20Ambani%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Narayana%20Murthy%26quot%3B%20promoting%20a%20fraudulent%20trading%20platform.%20The%20trust%20that%20these%20entrepreneurs%20have%20built%20in%20the%20public%20eye%20was%20misused%20to%20sell%20fake%20schemes.%20The%20internet%20is%20being%20flooded%20with%20countless%20stories%20of%20schoolboys%20sharing%20inappropriate%20images%20of%20peers%20and%20teachers.%20The%20psychological%20scarring%20that%20children%20will%20endure%20in%20their%20formative%20years%20is%20immense.%20As%20technology%20becomes%20more%20adept%20at%20cloning%20voices%20and%20faces%2C%20it%20will%20create%20even%20greater%20challenges%20for%20an%20ill-prepared%20society.%20News-driven%20deepfakes%20on%20%3Cem%3EX.AI%3C%2Fem%3E%20probably%20did%20influence%20US%20elections%2C%20and%20we%20will%20see%20the%20impact%20only%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20as%20AI's%20reach%20widens%2C%20shaping%20the%20kind%20of%20leaders%20our%20world%20will%20get%20in%20the%20future%2C%20all%20in%20the%20name%20of%20free%20speech.%20Ironically%2C%20we%20don't%20even%20know%20what%20%26quot%3Bfree%20speech%26quot%3B%20means%20for%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20Contrasting%20Approaches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20approach%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%20the%20US%2C%20where%20they%20are%20allowing%20the%20technology%20to%20evolve%20and%20reshape%20human%20society%20without%20regulation%2C%20creating%20a%20true%20'Wild%20Wild%20West'%20on%20steroids.%20On%20the%20other%20side%2C%20we%20have%20the%20EU%2C%20which%20has%20tried%20to%20erect%20AI%20superwalls%20with%20strict%20regulation%2C%20choosing%20to%20be%20late%20adopters.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20massive%20frustration%20among%20AI%20startups%20and%20innovators%2C%20who%20are%20fleeing%20the%20EU%20in%20droves.%20I%20think%20both%20approaches%20are%20flawed.%20AI%20is%20not%20just%20another%20technology%3B%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20fundamentally%20upend%20the%20status%20quo.%20It%20is%20critical%20that%20we%20embrace%20this%20challenge%20while%20preserving%20the%20best%20aspects%20of%20human%20society%20and%20allowing%20for%20the%20potential%20upsides%20that%20the%20AI%20revolution%20offers.%20For%20India%2C%20which%20is%20entering%20a%20hyper-growth%20phase%20over%20the%20next%2010-15%20years%2C%20missing%20the%20AI%20wave%20by%20following%20the%20EU%20model%20is%20not%20an%20option.%20Yet%2C%20it%20must%20avoid%20the%20broader%20disruptions%20that%20society%20is%20currently%20unprepared%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20Way%3A%20AI%20Sandboxes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%20changed%20how%20we%20lived%20and%20worked%2C%20the%20AI%20revolution%20will%20drive%20a%20fundamental%20shift%20in%20how%20we%20coexist%20with%20intelligence%20on%20tap.%20To%20ensure%20this%20intelligence%20is%20not%20malicious%20or%20introduces%20change%20too%20quickly%2C%20we%20need%20to%20test%20it%20rigorously%20-%20not%20only%20in%20labs%20but%20also%20in%20real-world%20applications%2C%20closely%20monitored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20Cities%20For%20AI%20Innovation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20may%20need%20to%20create%20pro-innovation%20AI%20regulation%20zones%20in%20an%20AI%20city%20where%20we%20can%20safely%20observe%20AI%20in%20action%2C%20influencing%2040-50%25%20of%20human%20workflows%20in%20a%20legally%2C%20digitally%2C%20and%20physically%20bounded%20environment.%20Such%20an%20AI%20city%2C%20constantly%20monitored%20and%20benchmarked%20for%20AI%20safety%2C%20could%20allow%20us%20to%20safely%20build%20bridges%20to%20the%20AI%20revolution%20before%20unleashing%20it%20fully%20into%20society%20at%20large.%20The%20way%20to%20achieve%20this%20is%20through%20a%20greenfield%20development%20with%20infrastructure%20built%20specifically%20for%20AI%2C%20bounded%20by%20a%20legal%20and%20regulatory%20framework%20conducive%20to%20human%20and%20AI%20innovation.%20An%20innovation-driven%20city%20could%2C%20for%20example%2C%20provide%20live%20sandboxes%20for%20autonomous%20mobility%20(lanes%20for%20driverless%20taxis%20and%20autonomous%20logistics)%2C%20autonomous%20charging%20stations%20for%20intelligent%20robots%2C%20next-generation%20AI-driven%20healthcare%2C%20logistics%2C%20manufacturing%20and%20education%2C%20and%20open%2C%20real-time%20data%20for%20AI%20innovators%20in%20city%20governance%20and%20financial%20services.%20It%20would%20be%20a%20place%20designed%20with%20future%20possibilities%20in%20mind-a%20place%20where%20we%20can%20watch%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20human-machine%20society%20unfold%2C%20open%20to%20innovation%20yet%20capable%20of%20triggering%20a%20limited%20safe%20mode%20if%20things%20go%20awry%2C%20supported%20by%20a%20digital-physical%20twin.%20Such%20a%20place%20could%20change%20the%20course%20of%20the%20AI%20revolution%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20unfold%20safely%20while%20supporting%20sustainable%20development.%20It%20should%20also%20be%20a%20place%20that%20fosters%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20human%20consciousness%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20blossom%20alongside%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20we%20in%20India%20create%20this%20cradle%20of%20innovation%20not%20just%20for%20ourselves%20but%20for%20humanity%20as%20a%20whole%3F%20A%20city%20where%2C%20as%20Arthur%20C.%20Clarke%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhether%20you%20are%20made%20up%20of%20silicon%20or%20carbon%2C%20both%20should%20be%20treated%20with%20equal%20respect%26quot%3B%3F%20AGI%20might%20not%20wipe%20out%20humanity%2C%20but%20Artificial%20intelligence%20combined%20with%20human%20stupidity%2C%20without%20the%20essential%20safety%20lock%2C%20could%20definitely%20lead%20to%20disastrous%20outcomes%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BUmakant%20Soni%20is%20cha