World%20University%20Rankings%202025.%C2%A0The%20QS%20Rankings%20for%20this%20year%20highlighted%20India's%20impressive%20upward%20trajectory%20in%20higher%20education%20across%20Asia.%20Two%20institutions%20have%20been%20placed%20within%20the%20top%2050%20and%20seven%20in%20the%20top%20100%20rankings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIIT%20Delhi%20has%20achieved%20the%20highest%20ranking%20for%20India%20moving%20up%20to%2044th%20place%20from%2046th%20last%20year.%20The%20institute%20had%20an%20impressive%20employer%20reputation%20score%20of%2099%25.%20IIT%20Bombay%20followed%20second%20with%20an%20employer%20reputation%20score%20of%2099.5%25%20and%20an%20academic%20reputation%20score%20of%2096.6%25.%20IIT%20Delhi%20ranks%20at%20the%2044th%20place%2C%20while%20IIT%20Bombay%20is%20the%20second%20best%20institution%20in%20the%20country%20with%2048th%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Petroleum%20and%20Energy%20Studies%20(UPES)%20achieved%20the%20most%20significant%20improvement%20among%20Indian%20institutions%2C%20climbing%2070%20spots%20to%20148th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20institutions%2C%20including%20IIT%20Madras%20(56)%2C%20IIT%20Kharagpur%20(60)%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(62)%2C%20IIT%20Kanpur%20(67)%2C%20and%20University%20of%20Delhi%20(81)%2C%20are%20placed%20in%20the%20top%20100.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstitutions%20such%20as%20IIT%20Guwahati%2C%20IIT%20Roorkee%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Chandigarh%20University%20(120)%2C%20UPES%20(148)%2C%20and%20Vellore%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20are%20placed%20in%20the%20top%20150.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Delhi%20has%20improved%20its%20ranking%2C%20moving%20up%20from%2094th%20to%2081st%2C%20achieving%20a%20high%20score%20of%2096.4%25%20in%20the%20International%20Research%20Network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnna%20University%20achieved%20a%20perfect%20score%20of%20100%20in%20the%20Papers%20Per%20Faculty%20indicator%2C%20emphasizing%20high%20research%20outp