ommission%20(UPPSC)%20has%20assured%20candidates%20of%20maintaining%20exam%20integrity%20and%20ensuring%20its%20sanctity%20as%20several%20students%20staged%20protested%20against%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20UPPSC%20exam.%20The%20commission%20also%20noted%20that%20to%20uphold%20the%20sanctity%20of%20its%20examinations%20and%20safeguard%20students'%20futures%2C%20exams%20are%20conducted%20exclusively%20at%20centres%20where%20the%20possibility%20of%20irregularities%20is%20entirely%20eliminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20from%20the%20commission%20accepted%20that%20in%20the%20past%2C%20various%20irregularities%20had%20surfaced%20at%20the%20remote%20exam%20centres%20creating%20uncertainty%20for%20the%20students.%20However%2C%20the%20commission%20has%20removed%20such%20centres%20to%20prevent%20this%20and%20create%20a%20merit-based%20examination%20process.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Provincial%20Civil%20Services%20(PCS)%20Preliminary%20examination%20will%20be%20conducted%20over%20two%20days%2C%20on%20December%207%20and%208%2C%20while%20the%20Review%20Officer%20(RO)%20and%20Assistant%20Review%20Officer%20(ARO)%20Preliminary%20examination%202023%20will%20be%20held%20in%20three%20shifts%20on%20December%2022%20and%2023.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnStudents%20protested%20against%20the%20UPPSC%20decision%20to%20conduct%20the%20RO-ARO%20and%20PCS%20preliminary%20exams%20on%20different%20dates.%20The%20students%20held%20a%20sit%20in%20protest%20at%20the%20UPPSC%20headquarters%20in%20Prayagraj.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMaintaining%20that%20the%20primary%20goal%20of%20the%20government%20and%20the%20Commission%20is%20to%20safeguard%20students'%20interests%20and%20ensure%20selection%20based%20on%20merit%2C%20%C2%A0the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20commission%20mentioned%20that%20they%20have%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20candidates%20informing%20them%20that%20certain%20Telegram%20channels%20and%20YouTubers%20are%20conspiring%20to%20postpone%20the%20UPPSC%