ction%20against%20the%20officers%20following%20a%20report%20by%20Chief%20Secretary%20Sarada%20Muraleedharan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gopalakrishnan%2C%20a%202013-batch%20officer%2C%20has%20been%20suspended%20for%20creating%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20named%20%26quot%3BMallu%20Hindu%20Officers%26quot%3B%20last%20month.%20Following%20a%20row%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20had%20claimed%20that%20his%20phone%20was%20hacked.%20According%20to%20officials%2C%20a%20forensic%20examination%20of%20the%20phone%20did%20not%20establish%20that%20it%20was%20hacked%20and%20found%20that%20the%20phone%20was%20formatted%20amid%20the%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThiruvananthapuram%20City%20Police%20Commissioner%20Sparjan%20Kumar%20stated%20that%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20the%20device%20was%20compromised%20because%20it%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Breset%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%202007-batch%20officer%20N%20Prashanth%2C%20the%20action%20followed%20his%20outburst%20against%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%20A%20Jayathilak%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post.%20He%20accused%20the%20senior%20officer%20of%20orchestrating%20baseless%20news%20reports%20against%20him.%20Mr%20Prashanth%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Jayathilak%20was%20working%20to%20undermine%20him%20by%20spreading%20unfounded%20allegations.%20He%20described%20the%20senior%20officer%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpsychopath%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outburst%20followed%20a%20media%20report%20that%20claimed%20several%20files%20of%20'Unnathi'%20--%20an%20initiative%20aimed%20at%20the%20welfare%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20--%20went%20missing%20during%20Mr%20Prashanth's%20tenure%20as%20its%20CEO.%20Mr%20Prashanth%20has%20earlier%20worked%20as%20Kozhikode%20District%20Collector%2C%20among%20other%20roles.%20He%20is%20quite%20active%20on%20social%20media%20and%20is%20popularly%20known%20as%20'Collector%20Bro'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Prashanth%20has%20told%20a%20news%20channel%20that%20he%20had%20not%20