-homan-receives-2015-presidential-rank-award%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EICE%3C%2Fa%3E.%20ICE%20also%20arrested%20and%20deported%20534%2C000%20convicted%20criminals%20who%20entered%20the%20US%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObama%20awarded%20Homan%20the%20Presidential%20Rank%20Award%20for%20Distinguished%20Service%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHoman%20served%20as%20acting%20head%20of%20ICE%20during%20Trump's%20first%20presidency%20and%20was%20a%20proponent%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bzero%20tolerance%26quot%3B%20family%20separation%20policy.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20and%20Tom%20Homan%20sit%20next%20to%20each%20other%20in%20a%20White%20House%20meeting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67324b8788cea3ba1c1fd8d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%20and%20Thomas%20Homan.%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHoman%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fmagazine%2Farchive%2F2022%2F09%2Ftrump-administration-family-separation-policy-immigration%2F670604%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Atlantic%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Caitlin%20Dickerson%20that%20he%20first%20pitched%20the%20idea%20of%20prosecuting%20parents%20who%20entered%20the%20US%20illegally%20and%20separating%20them%20from%20their%20children%20in%20order%20to%20deter%20families%20from%20attempting%20dangerous%20illegal%20border%20crossings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20wasn't%20to%20traumatize%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20was%20to%20stop%20the%20madness%2C%20stop%20the%20death%2C%20stop%20the%20rape%2C%20stop%20the%20children%20dying%2C%20stop%20the%20cartels%20doing%20what%20they're%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamili