g%20centre%20stage.%20However%2C%20Bhati%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20begun%20to%20shift%20that%20perception%2C%20even%20if%20just%20a%20little.%20For%20example%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20worked%20with%20Ganga%20and%20Sundar%2C%20a%20mother-daughter%20duo.%20To%20see%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20once%20lacked%20confidence%20and%20had%20never%20sung%20outside%20her%20home%20now%20performing%20at%20shows%20and%20private%20events%20is%20the%20biggest%20reward%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20speaking%20with%20Ganga%2C%20who%20is%20as%20sweet%20in%20conversation%20as%20she%20is%20bold%20in%20song%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20a%20family%20of%20musicians%2C%20and%20I%20learned%20singing%20from%20my%20mother%20and%20grandmother.%20But%20I%20never%20thought%20I%20could%20reach%20this%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20reassuring%20to%20see%20young%20women%20participate%20in%20our%20residency%2C%20to%20the%20point%20where%20their%20parents%20trust%20us%20enough%20to%20let%20them%20attend%20without%20accompaniment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhati.%20This%20trust%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20strong%20relationships%20they%E2%80%99ve%20built%20within%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeeping%20the%20music%20alive%3A%20Supporting%20artists%20through%20the%20pandemic%20and%20beyond%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20folk%20artists%2C%20their%20livelihood%20depends%20entirely%20on%20their%20ability%20to%20perform%2C%20but%20during%20the%20COVID%20lockdown%2C%20when%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20the%20stage%2C%20the%20impact%20was%20devastating%20for%20entire%20communities.%20To%20support%20them%2C%20Sharon%20facilitated%20a%20collaboration%20with%20My%20Mensa%2C%20a%20visual%20learning%20app%2C%20offering%20these%20artists%20opportunities%20for%20live%20music%20sessions.%20This%20initiative%20ensured%20that%20the%20artists%20were%20fairly%20compensated%2C%20while%20also%20driving%20increased%20app%20traffic%20and%20downloads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20had%20to%20sit%20at%20home%20and%20do%20some%20of%20the%20work%2C%20so%20we%20were%20fine%20doing%20it%20for%20free%2C%20but%20the%20artists%20needed%20to%20be%20paid%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20our%20only%20condition%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20peak%20months%20of%20COVID-19%2C%20they%20successfully%20hosted%20live%20sessions%20on%20the%20app%2C%20allowing%20every%20participating%20artist%20to%20receive%20compensation.%20This%20initiative%20also%20encouraged%20greater%20involvement%20from%20women%2C%20as%20it%20eliminated%20the%20need%20for%20them%20to%20travel%2C%20enabling%20those%20who%20had%20only%20sung%20for%20their%20families%20to%20showcase%20their%20talent%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202448px)%20100vw%2C%202448px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20experienced%20Rajasthani%20folk%20artist%20teaching%20young%20children%20the%20intricacies%20of%20traditional%20music%20at%20the%20Lok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20residency%2C%20promoting%20cultural%20preservation%20and%20knowledge%20transfer.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846.jpg%202448w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media