%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20was%20founded%20to%20take%20a%20pragmatic%20approach%20to%20help%20children%20with%20dyslexia.%20For%20the%20past%20three%20decades%2C%20it%20has%20been%20providing%20remedial%20help%20and%20support%20to%20children%20with%20dyslexia%20and%20their%20parents%20through%20the%20Ananya%20Learning%20and%20Research%20Centre%20(ALRC).%20They%20have%20also%20been%20actively%20working%20towards%20spreading%20awareness%20to%20the%20community%20at%20large%2C%20helping%20schools%20set%20up%20resource%20rooms%20and%20conducting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309309%2Fcentral-square-foundation-teachers-guide-improves-learning-outcomes-nipun-bharat-mission%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteacher%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20dyslexia%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20MDA%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20dyslexia%20is%20a%20hidden%20%5Blearning%5D%20disability%20that%20does%20not%20allow%20the%20child%20to%20perform%20to%20his%2Fher%20actual%20potential%2C%20the%20underachievement%20of%20an%20otherwise%20intelligent%20child%20is%20puzzling%20to%20both%20teachers%20and%20parents%20alike.%20Timely%20identification%20and%20appropriate%20help%20will%20ensure%20that%20these%20children%20continue%20their%20education%20and%20their%20potential%20is%20fully%20tapped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20with%20dyslexia%20could%20face%20challenges%20in%20their%20academic%20pursuits%20(especially%20in%20their%20school-going%20years)%20due%20to%20difficulties%20in%20reading%2C%20spelling%2C%20writing%20and%20or%20maths%2C%20despite%20their%20average%20to%20above%20average%20intelligence.%20Most%20often%2C%20parents%2C%20teachers%20and%20peers%20focus%20on%20these%20areas%20of%20deficits%20ignoring%20the%20talents%20these%20individuals%20could%20be%20bestowed%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%